                                        <h3>Essential Documents</h3>
                                        <p>
                                            Completed application form should reach the office with the attested copies of the following. 
<br>1. SSLC mark sheet – 2 copies. 
<br>2. PUC/ Plus Two/ Intermediate marks sheet – 2 copies  
<br>3. Certificates of higher qualification/ Degree/ Training/ computer etc. if any 
<br>4. Transfer Certificate from the school/ college last attended. 
<br>5. Birth Certificate. 
<br>6. Cast and income Certificate. 
<br>7. Medical fitness Certificate from a Registered Medical practitioner not below the rank of MBBS. 
<br>8 .Character and Conduct Certificate from the school/ College you have studied. 
<br>9. Recent Passport size photographs –6.


